### Simple Express App

This is a simple Express application built with Node.js. It provides basic CRUD operations with user authentication and task management. 
The app uses MongoDB for data storage and JWT (JSON Web Tokens) for user authentication.

### Features
- User Authentication (Login)
- Task Management (Create, Read, Update, Delete)
- JWT Authentication for protected routes
- Environment Configuration using dotenv
- Middleware for protecting routes

### Cloning command
- git clone https://github.com/Talha-crypto/simple_express_app.git

### Installations
- need Node installed
- npm install for installing the required packages

